race.comment: DON'T WINK (6) finds himself right back in grade today following strong efforts in Stakes company to begin this preparation. He was strong from the front in the Placid Ark first-up and coming back to 1200m looks ideal. Can roll forward and he would just need to hold his form to be winning. CONDUCIVE (12) looks a handy type on debut for the Grantham stable with CJP in the saddle. He's been with her all the way through, trialling her at every opportunity. Her last two trials have been very good and while she's drawn wide, she looks to have some class about her. BANNERED (1) can be in the finish first-up on the back of a nice trial. ENERGETIC (2) won't be far away third-up into the campaign.
